==18913==  mul                     7073                     7073          (100%)
==18913==   `- dbl                     7073                     7073      (100%)
==18913==       `- llo                     7073                     7073  (100%)
==18913==  ---------------------------------------------------------------------
==18913==  div                        7                        7          (100%)
==18913==   `- dbl                        7                        7      (100%)
==18913==       `- llo                        7                        7  (100%)
